    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And when I was on the train, I, I struck up-- some young soldiers struck up a conversation with me, you know, just because I didn't really look Jewish, so nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "What-- they were maybe 17, 18, 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And so, during the conversation, which is very-- it, it, it-- it's very interesting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "During the conversation, they said, well we had been on this and this and these and those kinds of maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "This was in May, '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they said, in August, we will probably go--",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
